        <remarks>
          <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <xref:System.Data.DataView.Sort%2A> can have two defaults based on the value of <xref:System.Data.DataView.RowFilter%2A> property. If <xref:System.Data.DataView.RowFilter%2A> is null or empty (that is, the value is not explicitly specified), the <xref:System.Data.DataRowView> in the <xref:System.Data.DataView> is sorted on the position or ordinal of <xref:System.Data.DataRow> in the <xref:System.Data.DataTable.Rows%2A> collection. The <xref:System.Data.DataView.Sort%2A> default, an empty string, causes a <xref:System.Data.DataRowView> in <xref:System.Data.DataView> to be sorted on the position or ordinal of <xref:System.Data.DataRow> in the <xref:System.Data.DataTable.Rows%2A> collection.  
  
 ]]></format>
        </remarks>
        <threadsafe />
        <returns>The sort to apply in the <see cref="T:System.Data.DataView" />.</returns>
      </Docs>
